title: A Study Run by Power Outages
description: A project in which I studied and made visualizations about different outages all across the United States across many years. I made a model to predict which cities are at high risk of power outages.

title: San Francisco's Summer Fog
description: A visualization in which we see a take about what factor contributes the most to the strange and wild fog during the summer in San Francisco.
